import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Sans, Serif, Display } from '../src'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"typography"}}>{`Typography`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sans"}}>{`Sans`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Sans size="1">Sans 1</Sans>
<Sans size="2">Sans 2</Sans>
<Sans size="3">Sans 3</Sans>
<Sans size="3t">Sans 3t</Sans>
<Sans size="4">Sans 4</Sans>
<Sans size="4t">Sans 4t</Sans>
<Sans size="5">Sans 5</Sans>
<Sans size="5t">Sans 5t</Sans>
<Sans size="6">Sans 6</Sans>
<Sans size="8">Sans 8</Sans>
<Sans size="10">Sans 10</Sans>
<Sans size="12">Sans 12</Sans>
<Sans size="14">Sans 14</Sans>
<Sans size="16">Sans 16</Sans>`} __scope={{props,Sans,Serif,Display}}>
  <Sans size="1">Sans 1</Sans>
  <Sans size="2">Sans 2</Sans>
  <Sans size="3">Sans 3</Sans>
  <Sans size="3t">Sans 3t</Sans>
  <Sans size="4">Sans 4</Sans>
  <Sans size="4t">Sans 4t</Sans>
  <Sans size="5">Sans 5</Sans>
  <Sans size="5t">Sans 5t</Sans>
  <Sans size="6">Sans 6</Sans>
  <Sans size="8">Sans 8</Sans>
  <Sans size="10">Sans 10</Sans>
  <Sans size="12">Sans 12</Sans>
  <Sans size="14">Sans 14</Sans>
  <Sans size="16">Sans 16</Sans>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={Sans} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"serif"}}>{`Serif`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Serif size="1">Serif 1</Serif>
<Serif size="2">Serif 2</Serif>
<Serif size="3">Serif 3</Serif>
<Serif size="3t">Serif 3t</Serif>
<Serif size="4">Serif 4</Serif>
<Serif size="4t">Serif 4t</Serif>
<Serif size="5">Serif 5</Serif>
<Serif size="5t">Serif 5t</Serif>
<Serif size="6">Serif 6</Serif>
<Serif size="8">Serif 8</Serif>
<Serif size="10">Serif 10</Serif>
<Serif size="12">Serif 12</Serif>`} __scope={{props,Sans,Serif,Display}}>
  <Serif size="1">Serif 1</Serif>
  <Serif size="2">Serif 2</Serif>
  <Serif size="3">Serif 3</Serif>
  <Serif size="3t">Serif 3t</Serif>
  <Serif size="4">Serif 4</Serif>
  <Serif size="4t">Serif 4t</Serif>
  <Serif size="5">Serif 5</Serif>
  <Serif size="5t">Serif 5t</Serif>
  <Serif size="6">Serif 6</Serif>
  <Serif size="8">Serif 8</Serif>
  <Serif size="10">Serif 10</Serif>
  <Serif size="12">Serif 12</Serif>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={Serif} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"display"}}>{`Display`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Display size="2">Display 2</Display>
<Display size="3t">Display 3t</Display>
<Display size="4t">Display 4t</Display>
<Display size="5t">Display 5t</Display>
<Display size="6">Display 6</Display>
<Display size="8">Display 8</Display>`} __scope={{props,Sans,Serif,Display}}>
  <Display size="2">Display 2</Display>
  <Display size="3t">Display 3t</Display>
  <Display size="4t">Display 4t</Display>
  <Display size="5t">Display 5t</Display>
  <Display size="6">Display 6</Display>
  <Display size="8">Display 8</Display>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={Display} /></MDXTag>
